  "body": "`Part of #9264 keycard sign-in epic (mark as checked there, when closing this issue)`\r\n\r\nThe \"Wrong passcode\" indicator should be displayed for 2.2 seconds and disappear (to be replaced with the number of attempts indicator https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/9285), as well as the red background of the dots below it.\r\n\r\nWhen the error appears **the device should vibrate** if possible.\r\n\r\nThe animation of the message should work as follows:\r\n\r\n```\r\nerror-mindicator-hidden: { scale: 0.9, opacity: 0 },\r\nerror-mindicator-shown: { scale: 1, opacity: 1 }\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe transition between those states:\r\n\r\n```\r\n{ duration: 0.1,\r\nease: \"easeInOut\" }\r\n```\r\nVideo:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"256\" alt=\"screen1\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3115606/67675996-8b226b00-f9bb-11e9-8428-ee89e44fe6f2.gif\">\r\n\r\nStatic image:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1153\" alt=\"Untitled5\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/3115606/67676507-9d50d900-f9bc-11e9-97e9-b81577a331c1.png\">\r\n\r\nFigma:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/dEIljL7UPbXgsZUA0Q4qlE5E/Onboarding?node-id=4566%3A12",
